# Aligned with clean_embedded.py
# Regenerable Keil/embedded build artifacts.

# Object and dependency files
*.o
*.obj
*.d
*.dep
*.crf
*.lst
*.lnp
*.plg

# Build reports and linked images
*.htm
*.html
*.build_log.htm
*.axf
*.elf

